    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in stunning shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in flawless condition, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
