    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely pristine, mint condition. Not a single scratch on the paint, the interior still has that fresh new-car smell, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m only selling because I\u2019m downsizing, but I really want it to go to someone who will love it as much as I have. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
