    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical condition. This specimen features the S54 3.2L high-pressure-cast iron block inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS solenoid have been serviced to ensure peak operational integrity. The chassis remains torsionally rigid, with the suspension geometry maintaining factory-spec kinematics. This is a rare, high-revving, naturally aspirated masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance.",
